    <item>
      <title>特鲁多警告加拿大企业推迟气候投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/canadian-firms-are-delaying-climate-investments-trudeau-is-warned</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份新报告警告说，加拿大在实现 2030 年排放目标方面面临着“关键问题”，因为由于该国气候政策未来的不确定性，企业正在推迟建设低碳项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/canadian-firms-are-delaying-climate-investments-trudeau-is-warned</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰富瑞表示，到 2030 年，印度市场价值将达到 10 万亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/india-market-value-to-reach-10-trillion-by-2030-jefferies-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 表示，根据其两位数回报率的历史以及持续经济改革的预期，到 2030 年，印度股市价值将增长一倍以上，达到 10 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/india-market-value-to-reach-10-trillion-by-2030-jefferies-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:59:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲咖啡贸易商敦促欧盟推迟森林砍伐规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/europe-s-coffee-traders-urge-eu-to-delay-deforestation-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲咖啡行业敦促欧盟推迟实施其开创性的森林砍伐规则，理由是这可能对数百万种植者造成毁灭性影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/europe-s-coffee-traders-urge-eu-to-delay-deforestation-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:59:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着通货膨胀的缓解，雀巢、达能试图赢回购物者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/nestle-forecasts-revenue-slowdown-as-inflation-eases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雀巢和达能正试图通过放宽价格上涨来鼓励购物者再次购买更多品牌食品，因为通货膨胀已从促使许多消费者选择更便宜的自有品牌的水平放缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/nestle-forecasts-revenue-slowdown-as-inflation-eases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 06:16:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
